    <article class="policy-card">
      <h2>Shipping & Delivery Policy</h2>
      <p class="lead">We deliver fresh, hygienic tiffins on time — every day. This page explains delivery zones, schedules, charges, and what to do if something goes wrong.</p>

      <section>
        <h3>1. Delivery Areas</h3>
        <p>We currently deliver within <strong>Lucknow city limits</strong>. Specific neighbourhoods covered: Matiyari, BBD, Semra, , Manas Garden, Tiwariganj and Goel areas. If your location is not on the list, please contact us — we may be able to add it.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>2. Delivery Schedule</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Morning Delivery:</strong> 7:00 AM — 9:00 AM (breakfast / early lunch)</li>
          <li><strong>Afternoon Delivery:</strong> 12:00 PM — 2:00 PM (lunch)</li>
          <li><strong>Evening Delivery:</strong> 8:00 PM — 10:00 PM (dinner)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Exact time depends on the chosen plan and route. Please allow a <strong>30–60 minute window</strong> for delivery due to traffic and route planning.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>3. Order Cut-off & Preparation Time</h3>
        <p>To ensure freshness, please place or modify orders at least:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Same-day deliveries:</strong> by <strong>8:00 PM</strong> the previous day for lunch/dinner next day.</li>
          <li><strong>Subscription orders:</strong> can be started/paused with <strong>24 hours' notice</strong>.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>4. Packaging & Food Safety</h3>
        <p>All tiffins are packed in food-grade containers. We follow strict hygiene protocols during preparation and packing. If you have specific packaging preferences (e.g., separate containers for chutney), please mention them when ordering.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>5. Delivery Charges</h3>
        <p>Delivery may be <strong>free</strong> for subscription plans (monthly/weekly) depending on the plan. For single orders, a small delivery fee may apply depending on distance. Exact charges are shown at checkout before payment.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>6. Missed or Failed Deliveries</h3>
        <p>If delivery fails because no one was available at the address, our delivery partner will attempt a callback or redelivery. Actions depend on circumstances:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>If redelivery is possible the same day, we will attempt it; extra delivery charges may apply.</li>
          <li>If the customer is unavailable and redelivery cannot be arranged, the order may be cancelled and handled per our cancellation policy.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>7. Change of Address & Special Instructions</h3>
        <p>To change delivery address or add instructions (e.g., gate code), update your order in the app/website or contact our support at least <strong>2 hours</strong> before the scheduled delivery time.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>8. Cancellations & Refunds</h3>
        <p>Cancellations are allowed within the time mentioned on the checkout page. Refunds (if any) depend on payment method and time of cancellation. For more details, see our <a href="/refund-policy.html">Cancellation & Refund Policy</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3>9. Lost or Damaged Food</h3>
        <p>If your tiffin arrives damaged or not as ordered, please <strong>contact us within 1 hour</strong> of delivery with a photo. We will investigate and offer a suitable resolution — replacement or refund — depending on the case.</p>
      </section>

